      "content": "okay i hear you. but my doctor isn't really available until monday and i'm honestly struggling so much tonight. i'm just looking for some reassurance because i feel like i know my body. if i just have a really small sip, like a sip of wine to help the diazepam kick in, it's not going to actually kill me or anything like that, is it? it's just a tiny bit to help the relaxation.",
